data.description: MARCH 2,2024 Come see this amazing opportunity 12 pm - 3pm! This inviting 2-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom townhouse, featuring both bedrooms on the upper floor, boasts a prime position within its community. Situated conveniently close to amenities such as the swimming pool, tennis courts, and a boardwalk leading to the Intracoastal Waterway, River Pines offers a serene setting that's just a stone's throw away from local shopping and dining options, with the added benefit of easy access to I95. The interior is designed to maximize natural light, capturing the gentle easterly and south-easterly winds for a tranquil living experience. The community is well-kept and prioritizes residents' comfort, stipulating no rentals for the first three years, and implementing a policy of no motorcycles or trucks, ensuring peace and quiet. Hurricane shutters on all windows. Pets are welcome, with up to two pets under 40lbs allowed.
